<p dir="auto">Note that the start of the <code>samtools mpileup</code> output differ from the
start of the <code>samtools depth</code> output. This is because <code>mpileup</code> performs
some filtering by default. In the case of this example, read pairs that
are not both mapped will be ignored. To count these “orphan” reads, use
the <code>--count-orphans</code> argument.</p>
<div class="highlight highlight-source-shell notranslate position-relative overflow-auto" dir="auto" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content="samtools mpileup -f genome/chrX.fa --count-orphans -s eg/ERR188273_chrX.bam &gt; ERR188273_mpileup_orphans.tsv
